						 <p>I've written a bunch of stuff now, with <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/maliceaf-author-ght">moderate success</a>, and I reckon it's high time I started writing more for myself than anyone else. This is the product of that. I love me some convoluted time stuff, if you can't already tell!</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Attributions,&nbsp;Inspirations,&nbsp;and&nbsp;Thanks</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Hide&nbsp;this</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I give my eternal thanks to the following people:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518200767" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stallmantic" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3472766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518200767" alt="Stallmantic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3472766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stallmantic" >Stallmantic</a></span>, for looking this over beforehand and giving me the confidence to post.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=571081&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518200767" alt="qntm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=571081)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" >qntm</a></span>, for writing <a href="https://qntm.org/destroyed">really cool off-site time-travel fiction</a>.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518200767" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" >A Random Day</a></span>, for writing <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/SCP-3780">really cool on-site time-travel fiction</a>.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fortunefavorsbold" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1552358&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518200767" alt="FortuneFavorsBold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1552358)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fortunefavorsbold" >FortuneFavorsBold</a></span>, for writing <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/iteration-0">a brilliant time-travel series</a> that I absolutely adore.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518200767" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" >Taffeta</a></span>, for providing the alternate MTF names.</li> <li>Chancellor Ptserfractal T. Glant, Conqueror of Worlds, for not deleting this during the Great Retroactive Literature Purge of 4056 AD.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1518200767" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:u